Gii thiu v UMAP

Khi nim

Uniform Manifold Approximation and Projection(UMAP) l mt k thut gim chiu d liu, tng t nh t-SNE, thng c s dng trc quan ha d liu. Ngoi ra, UMAP cn c th c s dng nh mt phng php gim chiu phi tuyn tng qut trong cc bi ton hc my.Thut ton UMAP c xy dng da trn ba gi nh chnh v cu trc d liu:

1.  D liu phn b u trn mt a tp Riemannian (Riemannian manifold);
2.  Metric Riemannian l hng s cc b (hoc c th c xp x l nh vy);
3.  ng phn phi (local connectivity) c kt ni cc b.

Mc tiu ca UMAP

UMAP c cc mc tiu sau:

  • Gim s lng bin: UMAP chuyn i d liu sang mt khng gian c s chiu thp hn, ph hp cho cc tc v x l v phn tch tip theo.

    • Gi li cu trc d liu: UMAP c gng bo ton c cu trc cc b (local structure) ln cu trc tng th (global structure) ca d liu trong khng gian mi.

    • Bo tn mi quan h phi tuyn: Khc vi PCA, UMAP c kh nng nm bt v biu din cc mi quan h phi tuyn gia cc im d liu.

    • Trc quan ha d liu: UMAP c bit hiu qu trong vic trc quan ha d liu nhiu chiu trong khng gian 2D hoc 3D, vi chnh xc v sc nt cao hn so vi nhiu k thut khc nh t-SNE.

Quy trnh thc hin UMAP

  1. Chun ha d liu (nu cn)

  2. Tm k hng xm gn nht cho mi im v xy dng th fuzzy biu din cu trc cc b

  3. Tnh ton xc sut kt ni gia cc im da trn khong cch v hm kernel

  4. Khi to im trong khng gian thp chiu v ti u ha th sao cho bo ton cu trc so vi th ban u

  5. Chiu d liu sang khng gian mi phc v trc quan ha hoc cc bc phn tch tip theo

ng dng UMAP vi b mtcars

B d liu mtcars cha thng tin v 32 mu xe vi 11 bin m t cc c im k thut:

  • mpg: Miles per gallon (hiu sut tiu th nhin liu)

  • cyl: S xi-lanh

  • disp: Dung tch xi-lanh

  • hp: M lc

  • drat: T s truyn ng sau

  • wt: Trng lng (1000 lbs)

  • qsec: Thi gian chy 1/4 dm

  • vs: Kiu ng c (0 = ch V, 1 = thng hng)

  • am: Kiu hp s (0 = t ng, 1 = s sn)

  • gear: S lng s

  • carb: S lng b ch ha kh

  mutate(
    engine_type = factor(vs, labels = c("V-shaped", "Straight")),
    transmission = factor(am, labels = c("Automatic", "Manual")),
    cylinders = factor(cyl)
  )

Nhn xt: - UMAP to ra mt biu din hai chiu t d liu mtcars, trong cc xe c c im k thut tng ng thng c phn b gn nhau trn mt phng. - Kt qu cho thy c s phn tch kh r rng gia cc loi ng c (engine_type), kiu hp s (transmission) v s xi-lanh (cylinders). - Quan st cho thy cc xe s dng ng c V-shaped c xu hng to thnh mt nhm ring bit, tng t vi cc xe c cng s xi-lanh.

Thc hin UMAP vi cc tham s khc nhau

library(uwot)
library(dplyr)
library(ggplot2)

run_umap <- function(n_neighbors_val, min_dist_val) {
  set.seed(42)
  result <- umap(mtcars_scaled,
                 n_neighbors = n_neighbors_val,
                 min_dist = min_dist_val,
                 metric = "euclidean")

  data.frame(
    x = result[, 1],
    y = result[, 2],
    engine_type = mtcars_labeled$engine_type,
    transmission = mtcars_labeled$transmission,
    cylinders = mtcars_labeled$cylinders,
    car = rownames(mtcars),
    n_neighbors = paste0("n = ", n_neighbors_val),
    min_dist = paste0("min_dist = ", min_dist_val)
  )
}

neighbors_values <- c(5, 15, 30)
min_dist_values <- c(0.01, 0.1, 0.5)

params_grid <- expand.grid(n_neighbors = neighbors_values,
                           min_dist = min_dist_values)

umap_all <- bind_rows(
  mapply(function(n, d) run_umap(n, d),
         params_grid$n_neighbors, params_grid$min_dist,
         SIMPLIFY = FALSE)
)

ggplot(umap_all, aes(x = x, y = y, color = engine_type)) +
  geom_point(size = 2.5, alpha = 0.8) +
  scale_color_viridis_d() +
  facet_grid(min_dist ~ n_neighbors, labeller = label_both) +
  labs(title = "UMAP vi cc gi tr n_neighbors v min_dist khc nhau",
       x = "UMAP dim 1",
       y = "UMAP dim 2",
       color = "Engine Type") +
  theme_minimal()

Nhn xt: UMAP cho thy mc tch bit gia hai loi ng c ph thuc vo gi tr n_neighbors v min_dist. Khi n_neighbors = 5 v min_dist = 0.1, hai nhm V-shaped v Straight c phn tch r rng nht. Khi tng n_neighbors, cc cm dn ha trn, c bit r n = 30. Gi tr min_dist cng ln th cm cng b dn tri, lm gim r nt. Tng th, t hp n_neighbors = 5, min_dist = 0.1 cho kt qu trc quan tt nht.

pca_result <- prcomp(mtcars_scaled, center = TRUE, scale. = TRUE)

# To dataframe vi kt qu PCA v nhn

  x = pca_result$x[, 1],
  y = pca_result$x[, 2],

)

Nhn xt khi so snh PCA v UMAP trn b d liu mtcars:

  • PCA cho thy c xu hng tch nhm gia ng c V-shaped v Straight, nhng cc im vn cn xen k, cm cha thc s r rng.
  • UMAP th hin r rng hn: hai nhm ng c c phn tch tt hn, cm khng b ln v c khong cch n nh. Kt lun : UMAP cho kt qu trc quan ha cm xi-lanh r rng v sc nt hn PCA.

B d liu USArrests cha thng tin v t l ti phm cho 50 bang ca Hoa K vo nm 1973 vi cc bin: - Murder: S v git ngi trn 100,000 dn - Assault: S v hnh hung trn 100,000 dn - UrbanPop: T l dn s th (%) - Rape: S v hip dm trn 100,000 dn

# Chun b d liu
state_names <- rownames(USArrests)
arrests_data <- USArrests

# Chun ha d liu
arrests_scaled <- scale(arrests_data)

set.seed(42)
arrests_umap <- umap(arrests_scaled, n_neighbors = 15, min_dist = 0.1)

# To dataframe t kt qu
arrests_umap_df <- data.frame(
  x = arrests_umap[, 1],
  y = arrests_umap[, 2],
  state = state_names
)

# Ghp d liu gc
arrests_umap_df <- cbind(arrests_umap_df, arrests_data)

northeast <- c("Maine", "New Hampshire", "Vermont", "Massachusetts", "Rhode Island", 
               "Connecticut", "New York", "New Jersey", "Pennsylvania")
midwest <- c("Ohio", "Indiana", "Illinois", "Michigan", "Wisconsin", 
             "Minnesota", "Iowa", "Missouri", "North Dakota", "South Dakota", 
             "Nebraska", "Kansas")
south <- c("Delaware", "Maryland", "Virginia", "West Virginia", "North Carolina",
           "South Carolina", "Georgia", "Florida", "Kentucky", "Tennessee", 
           "Alabama", "Mississippi", "Arkansas", "Louisiana", "Oklahoma", "Texas")
west <- c("Montana", "Idaho", "Wyoming", "Colorado", "New Mexico", "Arizona", "Utah",
          "Nevada", "Washington", "Oregon", "California", "Alaska", "Hawaii")

arrests_umap_df$region <- NA
arrests_umap_df$region[arrests_umap_df$state %in% northeast] <- "Northeast"
arrests_umap_df$region[arrests_umap_df$state %in% midwest] <- "Midwest"
arrests_umap_df$region[arrests_umap_df$state %in% south] <- "South"
arrests_umap_df$region[arrests_umap_df$state %in% west] <- "West"
arrests_umap_df$region <- factor(arrests_umap_df$region)

Nhn xt: UMAP biu din d liu USArrests trong khng gian 2D, bo ton cu trc cc b v ton cc tt hn PCA. Cc bang trong cng khu vc a l thng gn nhau trong khng gian UMAP. Cc bang c t l git ngi cao hoc dn s th cao c nhm li r rng. y l cng c mnh khm ph v pht hin mu trong d liu x hi hc.

Gim chiu d liu vi UMAP cho bi ton thc t

ng dng UMAP trong phn tch d liu ln

Trong phn ny, chng ta s tho lun cch UMAP c th c p dng trong cc bi ton thc t, c bit khi x l d liu c s chiu v kch thc ln.

Quy trnh x l d liu ln vi UMAP

  1. Lm sch v chun ha d liu
    • X l gi tr thiu, loi b ngoi lai
    • Chun ha cc bin s a v cng thang o
  2. Gim kch thc d liu (nu cn)
    • Vi tp d liu rt ln (hng triu mu), c th ly mu i din
    • C th kt hp gim chiu bng PCA (v d cn 50100 chiu) trc khi p dng UMAP
  3. p dng UMAP
    • Ty chnh cc tham s nh n_neighbors v min_dist iu chnh mc bo ton cu trc cc b hoc ton cc
    • C th hun luyn UMAP mt ln v p dng nh x ny cho d liu mi (generalizable)
  4. Gii thch v ng dng kt qu
    • Kt hp vi cc thut ton phn cm hoc trc quan ha
    • Hu ch trong phn tch khm ph, pht hin mu hoc bt thng

V d ng dng thc t ca UMAP

  1. Phn tch gene v biu hin protein
    • Gim chiu d liu gene (vi nghn chiu) phn tch cm t bo
    • Pht hin cc phn nhm chc nng hoc bnh l
  2. X l vn bn v ngn ng t nhin
    • Trc quan ha vector t hoc embedding cu vn
    • H tr khm ph cc nhm ch tng ng
  3. Pht hin gian ln v bt thng
    • Gim chiu d liu giao dch ti chnh
    • Nhn din cc im bt thng kh thy trong khng gian gc

Cc khuyn ngh khi s dng UMAP

  1. Tin x l d liu:
    • Bt buc chun ha nu d liu c thang o khc nhau
    • Khng cn loi b trng lp nh t-SNE
  2. Tham s quan trng:
    • n_neighbors: kim sot cc b, thng chn t 550
    • min_dist: kim sot khong cch ti thiu gia cc im sau khi chiu xung khng gian thp
      • Nh cm cht hn (ph hp phn cm)
      • Ln cu trc lan ta hn (bo ton ton cc)
  3. Kh nng nh x d liu mi:
    • UMAP c th lu nh x hc v d on cho d liu mi (transform())
  4. Tnh n nh v tc :
    • Kt qu thng n nh hn t-SNE
    • Nhanh hn ng k so vi t-SNE, nht l vi d liu ln

So snh UMAP vi cc phng php gim chiu khc

Phng php Tuyn tnh Bo ton cu trc Tc Kh nng m rng D gii thch ng dng chnh
PCA C Ton cc Nhanh Tt Cao Gim chiu, khm ph bin chnh
t-SNE Khng Cc b Chm Km Thp Trc quan ha cm d liu nh
UMAP Khng Cc b & ton cc Nhanh hn t-SNE Tt hn t-SNE Trung bnh Trc quan ha, phn cm
LDA C Phn bit theo nhn Nhanh Tt Cao Phn loi c gim st
MDS Ty Ton cc Trung bnh Trung bnh Trung bnh Phn tch tng ng
Autoencoder Khng Ty thuc m hnh Chm Tt Thp Gim chiu phi tuyn phc tp

Mt s lu khi s dng UMAP

  • Trnh hiu sai: UMAP khng bo ton khong cch tuyt i, m bo ton quan h hng xm gia cc im
  • Kt qu ph thuc vo tham s n_neighbors v min_dist nn th nghim nhiu gi tr
  • C th dng cho c d liu khng nhn v c nhn (semi-supervised)
  • Nu cn gii thch kt qu k, nn kt hp PCA hiu vai tr ca tng bin

Kt lun

UMAP l cng c gim chiu mnh m, c kh nng:

  1. Bo ton cu trc d liu cc b v ton cc tt hn t-SNE
  2. Tc x l cao, ph hp d liu ln
  3. C kh nng tng qut ha, p dng c cho d liu mi

UMAP khng ch gip trc quan ha d liu a chiu m cn h tr hiu qu cho cc bi ton nh phn cm, khm ph d liu v pht hin bt thng. y l cng c nn c u tin s dng khi lm vic vi d liu ln v phc tp trong thc tin.
